📦 Package Management
🔹 Debian/Ubuntu (APT)
apt-get update
apt install nginx -y
🔹 Best Practice 🚀
sudo apt-get update && sudo apt install nginx -y
🔹 RedHat/CentOS (YUM)
yum install nginx -y
⚙️ Service Management (systemctl)
systemctl status nginx
systemctl start nginx
systemctl stop nginx
systemctl restart nginx
systemctl enable nginx
🌍 Networking Tools
